// every bot needs a "random" topic as an entry point and fallback
! local concat = newline

> topic random inherits global_commands

    + start
    - Ribot Rivescript demo
    ^ `demo` for various demo features.
    ^ `asl` for basic examples.
    ^ building a `menu` or  displaying `media`.

    // choose something at random
    + gambit
    - {topic=asl}{@start}

    + *
    - <star>? {@gambit}

< topic
